"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月15日消息，花旗策略师预计，明年全球经济增长和通胀势头将放缓，并继续增持股票。包括Jamie Fahy在内的策略师说，他们预计增长势头放缓的原因是：随着当前周期的推进，风险回报已经恶化，预料新兴市场的通胀早于发达市场见顶。他们在报告中写道，对政府债券和信贷转向相对价值观点，并增加了一些新兴市场的风险，保持对基本金属的看空，对能源保持中性。\",\"timestamp\":1639816135,\"title\":\"花旗：预计2022年全球经济增长、通胀势头放缓\"},\"digest\":\"n-lKPJBrrm0Di-nFgD_ZafFiRnkZREvathq4-UAUOP8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xCCBb167704C05D09A5E128b0087B3aB1F2e7529d\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"RaGjqaVKG0k2o2NucYaKEV7NxX0wsgLR_YLaGCnxdfw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"RarWMp0ps8UQjeoMDEY7-f4Cy51l0Ra0SSLc09V8oQs\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"NvnWggvp1Wdt1umH2c9093pR5hHWyw-sqEtDfhX3LC-TSQgZTQEp57uo2U_HUI3ZgTVC-etlxYzoAIG_vhoUlw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x4d00ee77d2864b8aecbf2103b31208ab7f7504eae60150b2b6a0e6ddc292dd7c082ff49e201131029b0558d681b251110a7819de816605d5d61719bc910eeff61c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"RaGjqaVKG0k2o2NucYaKEV7NxX0wsgLR_YLaGCnxdfw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"RarWMp0ps8UQjeoMDEY7-f4Cy51l0Ra0SSLc09V8oQs\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"n-lKPJBrrm0Di-nFgD_ZafFiRnkZREvathq4-UAUOP8\"}"